OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775782987
OL,3,CEmperor penguins and Antarctic fur
OL,4,Cseals face extinction due to climate
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FEmperor penguins and Antarctic fur
OL,8,Fseals are both facing extinction
OL,9,Fbecause of climate change, according
OL,10,Fto a new conservation assessment.
OL,12,FThe populations of both species have
OL,13,Fplummeted in recent years due to a
OL,14,Floss of sea ice and reduced food
OL,15,Favailability.
OL,17,FThe assessment, from the International
OL,18,FUnion for Conservation of Nature
OL,19,F(IUCN), has prompted calls for urgent
OL,20,Faction to reduce planet-heating
OL,21,Fgreenhouse gas emissions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
