FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775782987
OL,3,CEmperor penguins and Antarctic fur
OL,4,Cseals face extinction due to climate
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThe emperor penguin, which is only
OL,8,Ffound in Antarctica, has moved from
OL,9,F"near threatened" to "endangered" on
OL,10,Fthe IUCN's red list as global warming
OL,11,Fdrives the early break-up and loss of
OL,12,Fsea ice.
OL,14,FNew projections show that the species'
OL,15,Fpopulation will halve by the 2080s
OL,16,Fwithout an abrupt and dramatic
OL,17,Freduction in planet-heating emissions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775782987
OL,3,CEmperor penguins and Antarctic fur
OL,4,Cseals face extinction due to climate
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThe birds require sea ice that is
OL,8,F"fastened" to the coastline, ocean
OL,9,Ffloor or grounded icebergs as a
OL,10,Fhabitat for their chicks, as well as
OL,11,Fduring moulting season when they are
OL,12,Fnot waterproof, so its loss can be
OL,13,Fdeadly.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, the Antarctic fur seal
OL,16,Fpopulations plummeted by more than 50%
OL,17,Fover 25 years, prompting its category
OL,18,Fto jump from "least concern" to
OL,19,F"endangered".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
