PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775782987
OL,3,CEmperor penguins and Antarctic fur
OL,4,Cseals face extinction due to climate
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThe southern elephant seal has also
OL,8,Fdropped in population and moved from
OL,9,F"least concern" to "vulnerable" on the
OL,10,Fred list, as bird flu threatens the
OL,11,Fspecies.
OL,13,FThe disease has affected four of the
OL,14,Ffive major subpopulations, killing
OL,15,Fmore than 90% of newborn pups in some
OL,16,Fcolonies and seriously impacting adult
OL,17,Ffemales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
