PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775782987
OL,3,CEmperor penguins and Antarctic fur
OL,4,Cseals face extinction due to climate
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThere are growing concerns that
OL,8,Fdisease-related mortalities of marine
OL,9,Fanimals will increased as the earth
OL,10,Fwarms, particularly in polar regions
OL,11,Fwhere animals have had less exposure
OL,12,Fto pathogens.
OL,14,FMartin Harper, chief executive of
OL,15,FBirdLife International, which co-
OL,16,Fordinated the emperor penguin
OL,17,Fassessment, said: "Climate change is
OL,18,Faccelerating the extinction crisis
OL,19,Fbefore our eyes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775782987
OL,3,CEmperor penguins and Antarctic fur
OL,4,Cseals face extinction due to climate
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,F"Governments must act now to urgently
OL,8,Fdecarbonise our economies."
OL,10,FThe WWF warned that Emperor penguins
OL,11,Fcould become extinct before the end of
OL,12,Fthis century, unless governments act
OL,13,Fnow to reverse the warming of
OL,14,FAntarctic waters.
OL,16,FDr Grethel Aguilar, IUCN director
OL,17,Fgeneral, said: "These important
OL,18,Ffindings should spur us into action
OL,19,Facross all sectors and levels of
OL,20,Fsociety to decisively address climate
OL,21,Fchange."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
