PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775782987
OL,3,CEmperor penguins and Antarctic fur
OL,4,Cseals face extinction due to climate
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,F"As countries prepare to gather at the
OL,8,FAntarctic treaty consultative meeting
OL,9,Fin May, these assessments provide
OL,10,Fessential data to inform decisions
OL,11,Fregarding this majestic continent and
OL,12,Fits awe-inspiring wildlife."
OL,14,FThe WWF, which has supported research
OL,15,Fefforts to monitor the species, is
OL,16,Fcalling for emperor penguins to be
OL,17,Fdesignated as a "specially protected
OL,18,Fspecies" under the Antarctic Treaty.
